# Optional. Only needed for the two AI-assisted features:
# - translating tech pack fields into EN/ZH
# - extracting embroidery specs from a Wilcom PDF worksheet
# The app works fully without this key; those two features just no-op.
#
# NOTE: this app calls the Anthropic API directly from the browser, which
# exposes whatever key you put here to anyone who loads the deployed page.
# Fine for local/internal use - for a public deployment, proxy this call
# through your own backend instead. See ROADMAP.md.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
